[[HTML5 Player]]


[DEVICES]
-------------------------------
7 parts for all:
1. piano client for pc x2
2. drum client for ipad
3. cymbals client for ipod touch
4. drum and cymbals player for pc
5. server by node.js which is used in 2 places: mobile and slides
6. slides
7. rhythm tester

[PAGES]
-------------------------------
http://192.168.1.56/
Slides: slides/index.html
Piano: piano/piano-sammy.html, piano/piano-zhuyao.html
Drum: drum/drum.html
Cymbals: cymbals/cymbals.html
Mobile Player: mobile-server/mobile-server.html
Server: node server/server.js
Rhythm Tester: rhythm-tester/rhythm-tester.html

[WORKFLOW]
-------------------------------
2 pianos(zhuyao & sammy)
set one piano(zhuyao) as a mobile device server
drum and cymbals connect to mobile device server to make sounds
set slides as a view server to receive all device hittings

[DEFAULT CONFIG]
-------------------------------
default gateway: 192.168.1.1
default slides ip: 192.168.1.56
default mobile server + piano(zhuyao) ip: 192.168.1.57

